#

Creamy Potato Soup

40 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupEasyComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy potato soup that's comforting and easy to prepare.

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 4 large, peeled and diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chives: for garnish
